import React from 'react'
const NewProject = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <button type="button" >New task</button>
        <form>
                <label>Nombre</label>
                <input value={""} type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Name task" ></input>
            <button type="button">Add task</button>
        </form>
        </>
    )
}

export default NewProject
